{"tid":2086204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[898 wechat,抖音]印度禁用中國手機程式　外交部：印方維護中企權益有責","createTime":"2020-06-30T08:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T08:28:24.000Z","uid":103207,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f31714f39ddadbbc9bd0f4542ef6103a572565","tid":2086204,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:05:00.000Z","msg":"印度政府宣佈基於國家安全，禁用59款中國手機應用程式。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅說，中方關注事件，正在查核相關情況。他表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">印度有責任維護中國企業的權益。</span><br />\n<br />\n遭<span style=\"color: red;\">印度政府禁用的應用程式包括抖音和微信等</span>。當局認為，這些應用程式以未經授權的方式竊取使用者數據，並且將數據傳送到印度以外的伺服器，影響到印度的主權和完整性，必須採取緊急措施。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2680000/2682932/20200630_TikTok_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2680000%2F2682932%2F20200630_TikTok_1024.png&h=8bb2ff4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23c171ededa648aa21ca081e9a87563a17e260e","tid":2086204,"uid":119393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:05:58.000Z","msg":"支那幾時用得fb, twitter, google?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bbb3e814cdc3a650fdf05adfcf1bb7f76189ee","tid":2086204,"uid":116087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"印度有責任維護中國企業的權益<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71db9d7da321c67aad7e2a3bca7bf3e390324fde","tid":2086204,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:06:12.000Z","msg":"又干預人哋內政"},{"pid":"3a71873f0cf319d01b4664b03e54a80b44c3f016","ti